data.description: Welcome to 517 W. Woodland Avenue, a great 3 bed, 2.5 bath, single family home located in sought after Springfield.  Enter the home into the foyer which opens to the spacious living room with wood beamed ceiling and a large front window that fills the space with natural light. Hardwood floors continue from the living room into the dining room and kitchen.  Eat-in kitchen boasts formica countertops and a door to the backyard and inviting patio where you can relax or entertain outside.  In the colder months sit fireside in the family room with a brick fireplace. A powder room completes the main level. Upper level primary bedroom offers multiple closets for ample closet space, hardwood floors and an en-suite with shower stall and tile floor.  Two additional bedrooms and a hallway full bath with tub/shower can also be found on the upper level.  Lastly, the lower level has been finished to offer additional living space with an expansive room for the perfect entertainment space, game room, home gym or whatever you can imagine! Some additional upgrades include a new 30 year roof, windows with lifetime warranty, gutters, shutters, hot water heater, chimney liner and siding! This home is conveniently located close to local parks, walking trails and other great amenities. Do not miss out on this great opportunity.
